  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To asses the precision of a score to predict chronic post surgical pain in patients
      undergoing inguinal hernia repair, abdominal hysterectomy, vaginal hysterectomy and
      thoracotomy. Prospective multicenter cohort study in 21 hospital in spain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
